&lt;h3 id=&#34;evaporation-minus-precipitation-emp-flux-2&#34;&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;markdownIt-Anchor&#34; href=&#34;#evaporation-minus-precipitation-emp-flux-2&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt; Evaporation minus precipitation (EMP) flux&lt;/h3&gt;
